  <description rain:description="General (short) project description" rain:type="description" type="3">RWH GIS mapping methodology for country and catchment level</description>
  <description akvo:type="5" rain:type="d_summary" type="1">The RAIN foundation tries to improve this understanding and sees potential in having a web-based tool to support their work. They envision a tool which: 
1. Explains why RWH mapping is essential and how to do it (with a simple, general method) 
2. Shows the results for the countries assessed in 2010 in an interactive webmap, as an example of potential results. 
3. Can later be extended by coupling to a hydrological model and climate scenarios; an exercise for which a quote is desired.</description>
